Package: ireader
Version: 1.0.0
Section: text
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: openjdk-17-jre | openjdk-18-jre | openjdk-19-jre, libasound2 (>= 1.0.16), libc6 (>= 2.27)
Maintainer: IReader Team <team@ireader.org>
Homepage: https://github.com/yourusername/ireader
Description: Modern eBook reader with offline text-to-speech
 IReader is a feature-rich eBook reader application with built-in
 offline text-to-speech support powered by Piper TTS. It supports
 multiple eBook formats and provides natural-sounding voices in
 20+ languages.
 .
 Features:
  * Offline text-to-speech in 20+ languages
  * Support for EPUB, PDF, and other formats
  * Customizable reading experience
  * Cross-platform compatibility
  * Privacy-focused (no cloud dependencies)
